    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "Dear [REDACTED]",
      "status": "redaction_marker_check"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Mr. Hoover has been called out of the city and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "asked me to acknowledge your letter to him, which was received",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "on November 13, 1961.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "Although Mr. Hoover would like to be of service,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "information in FBI files must be maintained as confidential through",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "a regulation of the Department of Justice. In this connection, the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "FBI is strictly an investigative agency of the Federal Government",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "and, as such, does not make evaluations nor draw conclusions",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "concerning the character or integrity of any organization, publica-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "tion or individual. Please do not infer either that we do or do not",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "have data in our files relating to the subjects of your inquiries.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "In light of the foregoing, you can be assured that this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "Bureau does not have a list of organizations of the type you discussed;",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "however, there is enclosed a list of groups designated by the Depart-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "ment of Justice as coming within the purview of Executive Order",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "10450. The material you enclosed is being returned to you under",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "separate cover.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
